d="$@A0pH0{zXfv9KFoAV00"><field name="TEXT">It says "Over broken ground the secret dwells, Guarded softly on silent shelfs, Pieces parted like scattered tricks, Count them true, they number six, Each a shard that locks and mends, Key fragments waiting where the riddle ends."</field></shadow></value></block></next></block></statement></block></statement></block></xml>